                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote xml:id="d1" type="miniature">
                                <locus target="#51v #103v #103v #161v #178v #216r #216v"/>
                                <desc>The manuscript contains several miniatures, apparently of a later date than the main production unit. The catalogue 
                                description does not state which miniatures have been drawn on which pages. The miniatures have the 
                                following content:
                                a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1044Prophet"/> of <persName ref="PRS1269Abraham"/>;
                                    a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> of <persName ref="PRS8491Samuel"/> and his lion;
                                    a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> of <persName ref="PRS10581Zamika"/>;
                                    a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> of <persName ref="PRS9162TaklaHa"/>;
                                    a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> of <persName ref="PRS3934Ewostate"/>;
                                    a scene with the caption <foreign xml:lang="gez">ደብረ፡ ምጥማቅ፡</foreign> written above, and written below
                                    <foreign xml:lang="am">ወይዘሮ፡ ወለተ፡ <gap reason="lost"/></foreign>;
                                    the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1030Trinity"/>;
                                    the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1068AdamandEveeatfruit">temptation of Adam and Eve</ref>;
                                    probably an <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1012Equestrian"/> of <persName ref="PRS3126Claudius"/> and
                                    <persName ref="PRS2548Basilide"/>;
                                    a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> of <persName ref="PRS8974Stephen"/>;
                                    the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1036MercyCovenant"/>;
                                    an <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/> of <persName ref="PRS7840Phanuel"/>;
                                    an <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/> of <persName ref="PRS8083Raphael"/> conquerring the
                                    <persName ref="PRS11330Devil"/>;
                                    a <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> of <persName ref="PRS4306GabraMa"/>.
                                </desc>
                            </decoNote>
                        </decoDesc>
                        
                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1" corresp="#h2">
                                        <locus from="209r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="LIT2894RepCh175"/></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ በመጽሐፈ፡ ሕይወት፡ ልኩዕ። ወለሥዕርተ፡ ርእስኪ፡ ጸሊም፡ ከመ፡ ሕብረ፡ ቋዕ።</seg></q>
                                 </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#1r"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript
                                        belongs to the church of <placeName ref="INS0101MadhaneAlam"/>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዳዊት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ <placeName ref="INS0101MadhaneAlam">መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም።</placeName></q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <desc>The name of <persName ref="PRS13071Estifanos"/> has been substituted by that of 
                                        <persName ref="PRS13075Iyasu"/> in <ref target="#a1"/>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <locus target="#96v"/>
                                    <desc>The names of several persons originally mentioned in the manuscript, possibly owners, 
                                        have been erased. Among these were <persName ref="PRS13072AsmaG"/>, a name ending with 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክርስቶስ፡</foreign>, and other illegible names, on <locus target="#96v"/> and 
                                    repeated every few pages.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e3">
                                    <locus target="#187v"/>
                                    <desc>The name of <persName ref="PRS13073Zamikael"/> is mentioned.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e4">
                                    <desc>The catalogue description speculates whether the depiction of Dabra Mǝṭmāq in
                                        <ref target="#d1"/> with the mention of 
                                        a woman, whose name began with <foreign xml:lang="gez">Walatta</foreign>, depicts the presentation
                                        of this manuscript to the convent, possibly <placeName ref="LOC2327DabraM"/>.</desc>
                                </item>
                            </list>
                            
